---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service — FARCO Marine" description="FARCO Marine Terms of Service. Read our terms and conditions for using our website and logistics services.">
  <Header slot="header" />
  <Footer slot="footer" />

  <PageHero title="Terms of Service" subtitle="Terms and conditions for using our website and services" />

  <section class="section-padding bg-navy-900">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="card animate-on-scroll space-y-8">
          <div>
            <p class="text-muted text-sm">Last updated: May 2026</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-heading mb-3">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
            <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
              By accessing and using the FARCO Marine website and services, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service ("Terms"). If you do not agree to these Terms, please do not use our website or services. These Terms apply to all visitors, users, and others who access or use our services.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-heading mb-3">2. Services</h2>
            <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
              FARCO Marine provides sea freight, road transport, customs clearance, warehousing, and related logistics services. All services are subject to availability and agreement on specific terms for each shipment. Quotes provided through our website are estimates and may be adjusted based on actual shipment details, market conditions, and carrier availability.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-heading mb-3">3. Quote Requests</h2>
            <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
              Submitting a quote request through our website does not constitute a binding contract. Quotes are provided for informational purposes and are subject to confirmation. A binding agreement is formed only when both parties agree to specific terms and conditions for a particular shipment in writing.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-heading mb-3">4. User Responsibilities</h2>
            <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">By using our services, you agree to:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-muted space-y-2 ml-4">
              <li>Provide accurate and complete information for all shipments</li>
              <li>Comply with all applicable laws and regulations</li>
              <li>Properly declare all goods, including hazardous materials</li>
              <li>Ensure all cargo is properly packaged and labeled</li>
              <li>Pay all applicable charges and fees on time</li>
              <li>Not use our services for any illegal or unauthorized purpose</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-heading mb-3">5. Shipping Terms</h2>
            <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
              All shipments are subject to the terms agreed upon in the specific shipping contract or bill of lading. Transit times are estimates and not guaranteed unless explicitly stated. FARCO Marine is not liable for delays caused by factors beyond our control, including but not limited to weather, port congestion, customs inspections, strikes, or acts of God.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-heading mb-3">6. Liability and Insurance</h2>
            <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
              FARCO Marine acts as a freight forwarder and logistics service provider. Our liability for loss or damage to cargo is limited to the terms specified in the applicable shipping contract and governed by international conventions (such as the Hague-Visby Rules). We strongly recommend that all shipments be covered by appropriate cargo insurance. We are not liable for indirect, incidental, or consequential damages.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-heading mb-3">7. Payment Terms</h2>
            <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
              Payment terms are specified in individual shipping agreements. Unless otherwise agreed, payment is due upon receipt of invoice. We reserve the right to charge interest on overdue payments and to suspend services for accounts in arrears. All prices are subject to change without prior notice.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-heading mb-3">8. Intellectual Property</h2>
            <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
              All content on the FARCO Marine website, including text, graphics, logos, images, and software, is the property of FARCO Marine or its content suppliers and is protected by intellectual property laws. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works from our content without written permission.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-heading mb-3">9. Website Use</h2>
            <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">You agree not to:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-muted space-y-2 ml-4">
              <li>Use the website in any way that violates applicable laws</li>
              <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to any part of the website</li>
              <li>Interfere with or disrupt the website's functionality</li>
              <li>Upload malicious code or content</li>
              <li>Collect user information without authorization</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-heading mb-3">10. Disclaimer</h2>
            <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
              The website and its content are provided "as is" without warranties of any kind, either express or implied. We do not warrant that the website will be uninterrupted, error-free, or free of viruses. Information on the website is for general purposes only and should not be relied upon for specific shipping decisions without direct consultation.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-heading mb-3">11. Governing Law</h2>
            <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
              These Terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the jurisdiction in which FARCO Marine is registered. Any disputes arising from these Terms shall be resolved through good-faith negotiation and, if necessary, through binding arbitration.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-heading mb-3">12. Changes to Terms</h2>
            <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
              We reserve the right to modify these Terms at any time. Changes will be effective immediately upon posting to the website. Your continued use of the website after changes are posted constitutes acceptance of the modified Terms.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-heading mb-3">13. Contact</h2>
            <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
              For questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us at:
            </p>
            <div class="mt-3 space-y-2">
              <p class="text-muted"><span class="text-heading font-medium">Email:</span> info@farcomarine.net</p>
              <p class="text-muted"><span class="text-heading font-medium">Company:</span> FARCO Marine</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
